        <extension url="urn:poc:discharge-summary">
          <valueString value="Mrs. Delacroix admitted with right lower lobe pneumonia and acute-on-baseline delirium (CAM positive). IV co-amoxiclav x48h then oral switch; SpO2 96% on RA by day 3. Delirium management: non-pharmacological reorientation, avoided sedatives, early mobilisation with PT. Cognitively back to baseline at discharge; CXR improved. Geriatrics follow-up 2 weeks; cognition reassessment at 1 month." />
